  "description": "Alterations including erection of single-storey rear extension with green roof and terrace incorporated at first-floor level; Installation of door and replacement windows along the rear elevation at first-floor level; Installation of spiral staircase leading from first-floor terrace to rear garden",
  "decision_date": "23/12/2022",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-5f6f63c9-7fff-9ffb-ed27-4a3e7ed0d001&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed terrace, by reason of its size and position, would result in the loss of privacy and general amenity to the adjoining properties, which would adversely affect the amenity of the neighbouring occupiers.  As such, the proposal would be contrary to policies D3 and D4 of the London Plan (2021), Policies LP1 and LP2 of the Local Plan (2020) and the stipulations of the council&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-1a2d2ef3-7fff-2af6-b3b1-da6dcbf4ddb9&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, due to the introduction of a first-floor terrace and brick visual screens, would be considered a bulky and incongruous form of development that would harm the character of the immediate area, and would fail to complement the original design of the host property. The proposed development is considered unacceptable in regard to design and fails to comply with Policies D3 and D4 of the London Plan (2021), LP1 and LP2 of the Hackney Local Plan (2020) and the stipulations of the council&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
  "development_type": "Other house holder developments"
